title: Google\Cloud\DataCatalog\V1\EntryGroup
name: EntryGroup
description:
Entry group metadata.

An EntryGroup resource represents a logical grouping of zero or more Data Catalog [Entry][google.cloud.datacatalog.v1.Entry] resources.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.datacatalog.v1.EntryGroup

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: The resource name of the entry group in URL format. Note: The entry group itself and its child resources might not be stored in the location specified in its name.

params.name: data.display_name
params.description: A short name to identify the entry group, for example, "analytics data - jan 2011". Default value is an empty string.

params.name: data.description
params.description: Entry group description. Can consist of several sentences or paragraphs that describe the entry group contents. Default value is an empty string.

params.name: data.data_catalog_timestamps
params.description: Output only. Timestamps of the entry group. Default value is empty.
